        &lt;p&gt;
I can replicate the 404 error. Follow steps below
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Click on add a new dataset
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Name it and put an incorrect character in tag field "e.g. " :"
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Click on 'Next: Add Data'
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Error message shows, wipe tag field (i.e. delete " : " until field is blank
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Click in 'Next: Add Data" again
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;
      </description>
